        },
        "image_with_text_QCfPjA": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1_cb146a69-b40c-411c-979d-bc20bc52bfe4.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Each corner of the store tells a story. The soft lighting brings out the brilliance of every diamond, the textures of the interiors echo modern elegance, and the warmth of the staff makes it all feel deeply personal. From custom <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Engagement Rings\">engagement rings</a> to <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-jewellery\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Jewellery\">lab grown diamond jewellery</a> in Chembur, each creation celebrates Indian</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-38ct-kite-shape-pear-cut-diamond-ring",
              "0-38ct-round-diamond-channel-eternity-band"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3UC84m": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p> craftsmanship with a global aesthetic.</p><p>As the doors to our store opened, the murmur, the glint of diamonds, and the elegant fresh flowers stood as symbols that, in a very short period of time, we delivered our promise of being extraordinary for our extraordinary clientele. <br/>As the ribbon was cut, it symbolized more than opening the store, but a new chapter in Lucira Jewelry’s story. The lighting of the Samay candle brought warmth and light into the space, reflecting Lucira’s philosophy of beginning every new chapter with gratitude and purpose. Vandana and Rupesh Jain, the founders of Lucira Jewelry delivered speeches about the vision of Lucira Jewelry and their gratitude towards all those who are part of this journey. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JN6bYV": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Lucira Jewelry’s Store Offers | Luxurious Diamond Jewelry Store in Mumbai",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What Lucira Jewelry’s Store Offers | Luxurious Diamond Jewelry Store in Mumbai</h2>",
            "custom_id": "store",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_wpU8KJ": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_466d3634-5667-4464-804c-94605dc3aec5.png",
            "text": "<p>Every Lucira diamond is crafted with precision and purpose. Our experience store reflects the same. Here, every visitor is invited to feel, learn, and personalize their jewelry journey with services designed to make your experience truly special. Our affordable diamond jewellery shop Chembur maximizes our customers’ satisfaction, we always go the extra mile to provide more than expected. At Lucira’s certified lab grown diamonds <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/chembur-store\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Chembur Store\">Chembur store</a>, we provide some essential services such as free <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/blogs/stories/engagement-ring-engraving-ideas\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Engraving Ideas\">engraving</a>, free repair, free diamond testing, and free diamond jewelry cleaning. Our bespoke services alleviate all customer worries and confusion. More than that, our jewelry experts are always happy to help customers make the right decision, making every purchase enjoyable rather than a task. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "column",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-318ct-round-toi-et-moi-ring",
              "0-32-carat-round-diamond-two-tone-gold-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
