        },
        "image_with_text_XhUrdK": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3.png",
            "text": "<p>Crafted out of gold and platinum, Lucira’s fine jewelry is designed to sparkle forever. With Lucira’s exclusive diamond cuts, our collection is elegant, timeless and sustainable. With lab grown diamond jewelry, we make luxury more accessible with add-on services like fast shipping so that your special pieces arrives on time for your grand days. Our SGI and IGI certified lab grown diamond jewelry comes in a plush, luxuriously wrapped jewelry box. At Lucira Jewelry’s store, you can find a ring sizer to get the perfect ring, but we go beyond that. We understand that with various cuts, shanks, carats, its nearly impossible to choose one favorite piece - so with our Ring Builder Kit, you can combine your choice of shank easily with the cut and carat you are looking for because why should buying jewelry be stressful, when it can be super easy and fun!  </p>",
            "layout_direction": "column",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": [
              "0-44ct-half-eternity-pave-diamond-band",
              "0-450ct-heart-round-diamond-toi-et-moi-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_R7MTiW": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Crafted out of gold and platinum, Lucira’s fine jewelry is designed to sparkle forever. With Lucira’s exclusive diamond cuts, our collection is elegant, timeless and sustainable. With lab grown diamond jewelry, we make luxury more accessible with add-on services like fast shipping so that your special pieces arrives on time for your grand days. Our SGI and IGI certified lab grown diamond jewelry comes in a plush, luxuriously wrapped jewelry box. At Lucira Jewelry’s store, you can find a ring sizer to get the perfect ring, but we go beyond that. We understand that with various cuts, shanks, carats, its nearly impossible to choose one favorite piece - so with our Ring Builder Kit, you can combine your choice of shank easily with the cut and carat you are looking for because why should buying jewelry be stressful, when it can be super easy and fun!  </p>",
