        },
        "rich_text_fQDHnE": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Make The Most Out Of The Omnichannel Experience ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Make The Most Out Of The Omnichannel Experience </h2><p>At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira jewelry</a>, we want to make luxury deeply personal, intuitive, and seamless. With our seamless online experience with customization options and virtual talk with our experts, our store becomes an extension of this luxurious experience with free engravings and in-person expert consultancy. No matter where you are, your shopping should be easy and fun to be a part of your milestone celebrations. So, we bring to life a store experience that mirrors our online experience - simple, elegant, enjoyable and filled with services that the customer is looking for. </p>",
            "custom_id": "omnichannel",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_yYBrjb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion</h2><p>Our Mumbai jewellery store in Chembur will hold a very special place for us. With the love of its community and the dedication of its team, Lucira Jewelry is ready to deliver its promises. With a seamless experience online, the store blends the omnichannel experience to enhance customer experience, to undoubtedly make decisions while investing in luxury. </p>",
